animals.Description:
Sage is a handsome boy whose soulful green eyes stop his admirers in their tracks.

He is a gentle sweetheart who loves people; 
Playful, but also happy to relax by your side;
Green-eyed heartbreaker with a thoughtful nature;
Eager to learn and food‑motivated;
Perfect mix of cuddle buddy and adventure partner

Sage is still young, so he’s ready to grow into the best version of himself with someone who will guide him with kindness.

tIf you’re looking for a dog who will adore you, make you laugh, and look at you like you hung the moon, Sage is your boy.
